    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a great start, really hits the tone i'm looking for. can you expand on that? like, specifically address why the common counter-argument about meritocracy is basically a fallacy in this context? i want to show how the idea of \"working hard to get ahead\" doesn't actually work when the system is rigged.",
